{"bangumi":{"date":"2017-07-03","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/53/49/192252_L9Ip9.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/53/49/192252_L9Ip9.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/53/49/192252_L9Ip9.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/53/49/192252_L9Ip9.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/53/49/192252_L9Ip9.jpg"},"summary":"在商业区附近的某条商店街角落，有栋挂着狗招牌的住商混合大楼，那间店就在那里的地下一楼。门上画了猫咪图案的餐馆──“猫咪西餐厅”。创业五十年以来，一直持续满足商业区上班族们的胃。虽然是西餐厅，但西餐以外的菜单也非常丰富，是间只有这点勉强称得上特征的普通餐厅。这么一间不起眼的小餐厅，在每周六都会对外公休，但是其实在这天都要迎接“异世界客人”的光顾：每到这天，店内的墙上就会出现一道门，这群客人不论是人族、魔族、鬼族、精灵族、蜥蜴人族、吸血鬼族、兽人、传说的魔龙（！？），都会从“门内”光临！","name":"異世界食堂","name_cn":"异世界食堂","tags":[{"name":"2017年7月","count":721,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美食","count":601,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻小说改","count":585,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SILVERLINK.","count":518,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美食番","count":501,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":457,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":411,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":352,"total_cont":0},{"name":"料理","count":341,"total_cont":0},{"name":"异世界","count":253,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2017","count":243,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻改","count":217,"total_cont":0},{"name":"异世界食堂","count":174,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小说改","count":70,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":58,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神保昌登","count":51,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":47,"total_cont":0},{"name":"泡面番","count":40,"total_cont":0},{"name":"诹访部顺一","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2017年","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SILVER_LINK.","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SILVERLINK","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"单元剧","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"諏訪部順一","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"后宫","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"杉田智和","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"犬塚惇平","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"上坂すみれ","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2017夏","count":3,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名